'''''Canja de Goa'''''  (Goencho sop) ek nomunedar [[Bharoti-Purtugez]] jevnna khannacho sop [[Goean]]to zavn asa, zo ekdam [[Purtugez Bharotantlo]] ek prant aslo, zachi sfurt [[Purtugez]] [[sop]]achi zavn asa.<ref name=cherie>Cherie Y. Hamilton, ''"Os sabores da lusofonia: encontros de culturas"'', Senac 2005, {{ISBN|8573594071}}</ref>

Tache toiarent [[kombiechem mas]], thollavim [[chevrisam]], [[piav]], [[losunn]], [[tandull]], [[udok]] ani [[mitth]] vaportat. He soglle jinos ektthaim eka lhan tovear vo eka pressure cookerant randtat. Xevttim, [[kombiechea mas]]achea [[hadd]]ancho kosai tantunt ghalpant ieta.

[[Goea]]nt, porompore pormonnem, to [[zolm ditolea ostoream]] khatir toiar korpant ietalo. Poilea zolmank, sasumai aplea sunank ek port wine hachea soreachi battli ani so kombeo dhaddttaleo, jeo ho sop toiar korpant vaportale, kiteak oxem korop avoiank ani bholaiki mellovpak borem jevonn somzotale.

Tem sumar sokallchea 11 vorancher, kallche koddie, godd [[toran]]che [[chettne]] ani [[kharea]] sangatak, ghevpant ietalem. Thodde favtti, tem mollamni bhurgeam koddlean, tanchea avoi-bapaink ani tanche poros vhodd piraiechea bhavonddank je thoim vavurtale, tankam ek matiechea aidonant patthovpant ietalem..

